Per Charles' comment in CONF-9367, we could provide better access to crash logs by storing them separate to the main application log. Recommend a sub-dir of conf-home with a catchy name, files inside will be keyed with a UUID. This opens the door for an Admin action to view individual crash logs and potentially resend or bulk-send them to support.
